    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Overall campus is soo big about 175 acres, so their is.a freedom to roam around anywhere you want.",
          "name": "rajas attarde",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "There are 2 grounds in the campus 1 for the cricket matches and another one for football and basketball, also there is swimming pool.",
          "name": "Jayesh Punde",
          "course_tag_name": "BE {Lateral}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Location of this college campus is on the mountain.",
          "name": "Shantanu Prafull Dalvi",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Campus life is amazing, campus is located on the mountains so the view you get to see is beautiful. There are many places near the campus where you can go for a trip with your friends. In campus there are general stores and cafes.",
          "name": "Jayesh Punde",
          "course_tag_name": "BE {Lateral}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Teaching faculty is very supportive and placements are average.",
          "name": "Jayesh Punde",
          "course_tag_name": "BE {Lateral}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Good scenery from the tip of hill and fresh air are the only thing that could be missed.",
          "name": "rajas attarde",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Hostel and mess facility provided near college building",
          "name": "Sumit Gudle",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Specific departments are located at specific building",
          "name": "Sumit Gudle",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Campus is picturesque and beautiful. Campus itself present in the mountains so the environment is very good.",
          "name": "Vishal More",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "The campus life is good the college is located lonavala in the nature is surrounded the campus",
          "name": "Gopal Santosh Karhale",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "College ambiance was too good in rainy season",
          "name": "Hitesh mohite",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "The college is outside of city that is about 4-5 kms.",
