          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Compared to F.E the S.E. college biulding is far away from hostel",
          "name": "Sumit Gudle",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Only 5 courses are included i.e comp, IT, E&TC, electrical and mech engg",
          "name": "Sumit Gudle",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Attendance issue in the college mandatory 75% attendance is compulsory",
